1
00:00:29,940 --> 00:00:31,456
Do you want to go home yet?

2
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:36,872
I still want to stay here with you.

3
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:08,328
What’s this now?

4
00:01:11,180 --> 00:01:15,352
We’ve only been a couple for a few hours and you’re already pushing me away?

5
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:17,472
You’re bored of me already, aren’t you?

6
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,712
Not at all.

7
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:22,720
You’re so sweet.

8
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:31,840
I’m not bored of you,

9
00:01:32,660 --> 00:01:34,256
and I never could be.

10
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:42,992
Do you know how long I’ve been waiting for this day?

11
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:49,168
From now on,

12
00:01:51,090 --> 00:01:52,696
let’s be happy together.

13
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:55,616
Every single day.

14
00:01:58,180 --> 00:02:02,136
Hmm, we’re going to be happy every single day.

15
00:02:05,390 --> 00:02:06,680
I love you, P'Chat.

16
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,008
I love you too, Ran.

17
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:52,248
Does he have guests?

18
00:02:52,896 --> 00:02:55,300
Yes, Ma'am. They’ve been here since this afternoon.

19
00:02:55,336 --> 00:02:58,792
Mr. Wichai said that as soon as you returned, you should go in to see him.

20
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:00,768
Ah,

21
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:03,528
let go.

22
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:05,040
Okay.

23
00:03:18,250 --> 00:03:20,344
Hey! Dad, what are you doing?

24
00:03:20,376 --> 00:03:24,184
What? Is it wrong for a dad to want to hug his own daughter?

25
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:28,176
Uncle, what are you talking about?

26
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:31,368
I’ll let your mother tell you the story herself.

27
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:32,792
Mom!

28
00:03:38,890 --> 00:03:40,160
Ranya, my daughter

29
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,248
Mom! How did you get here?

30
00:03:54,024 --> 00:03:56,020
What is going on?

31
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:01,488
This is Jintana. She’s my ex...

32
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:03,320
and she’s Ranya’s mother.

33
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,000
Your ex?

34
00:04:07,410 --> 00:04:08,576
Yes.

35
00:04:10,232 --> 00:04:11,832
What is the meaning of all this?

36
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:17,216
Why didn’t you ever tell me about this, Mom?

37
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,640
I am truly sorry

38
00:04:22,136 --> 00:04:24,140
for never telling you the truth.

39
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,272
I had my reasons,I really did.

40
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:30,256
But look.. Now you have everything,

41
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:35,696
a father, a mother, and an older sister.

42
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:45,472
Jintana and I were together before I was forced into an arranged marriage with Pimprapha.

43
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:49,120
And Ranya... you are our daughter.

44
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:12,192
From the very first day I brought you into this house,

45
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:16,640
it was because I knew you were a relative of Jintana, my ex.

46
00:05:17,060 --> 00:05:18,496
I felt pity for you.

47
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:24,088
But I’m blessed by the heavens.

48
00:05:24,670 --> 00:05:27,384
Jintana returned and told me the whole truth,

49
00:05:27,416 --> 00:05:31,200
that you are actually my own daughter with her.

50
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:40,520
That is why I felt such a bond with you from the moment we met.

51
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,112
So dad,  have you done a DNA test yet?

52
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:47,616
Why do I have to?

53
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:50,352
Do you not trust in me?

54
00:05:51,110 --> 00:05:52,744
It’s just something that should be done as a precaution, don't you think?

55
00:05:54,208 --> 00:05:56,210
You are exactly like your mom.

56
00:05:56,616 --> 00:05:58,620
Everything you do has to be about business.

57
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:02,152
Why! Are you afraid your sister is going to steal the company from you?

58
00:06:02,864 --> 00:06:04,860
It’s not like that, Dad.

59
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:06,600
We just need to check first.

60
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:08,784
We don’t know who we can actually trust.

61
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:22,200
Here are the DNA test results.

62
00:06:22,232 --> 00:06:24,488
I had them done back when Ranya was still a child.

63
00:06:35,220 --> 00:06:36,688
Then why don't we just do a new one?

64
00:06:37,020 --> 00:06:40,568
Um...Excuse me, I have to leave.

65
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:42,048
Ran.

66
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,576
Let her go.

67
00:09:15,310 --> 00:09:17,048
I’ve brought some orange juice.

68
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:18,944
May I come in?

69
00:09:41,850 --> 00:09:43,384
Can I sit with you?

70
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,136
Yes.

71
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:54,928
Your eyes are all swollen.

72
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:58,152
Come here.

73
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:11,888
this will make you feel better,

74
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:14,632
just like when you were little.

75
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:17,400
Doesn't that feel nice?

76
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:20,616
That’s nice.

77
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:24,192
Come over here, dear.

78
00:10:26,616 --> 00:10:30,208
Then you should go get dressed up nicely.

79
00:10:30,512 --> 00:10:32,510
Your dad is taking us both out.

80
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:35,120
Where are we going?

81
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,216
I don't know yet.

82
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:40,520
But I’m sure your dad will tell us soon.

83
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,152
Yes.
